title: Shaq’s 3-pointer at LSU might be high point of Tigers’ 2017 season | NCAA Basketball | Sporting News
text:
February 13, 2017 8:06am EST February 13, 2017 8:06am EST Basketball, News, English, Shaquille O'Neal, LSU Tigers Shaquille O'Neal was back in Baton Rouge this weekend, reminding fans of 9-15 LSU what they're missing. Shaquille O'Neal (Getty Images) 
Updated at 8:06 a.m. ET 
Updated at 8:06 a.m. ET 
Shaquille O'Neal was back in Baton Rouge, La., this weekend, reminding LSU fans what they're missing. 
O'Neal, who played at LSU from 1989-92, turned back the clock — Notorious B.I.G. shirt included — and stepped into a 3.
